definitions.definition: To overthink ; to treat as being deeper ( “ more profound, significant ” ) than in reality.
examples: ― Ugh, why are these road markings so awfully arranged? ― Quit deeping it bro, just drive, innit.

definitions.definition: To think about , especially deeply ( “ profoundly ” ) ; to consider .

main_definition: ( slang , MLE , transitive ) To overthink ; to treat as being deeper ( “ more profound, significant ” ) than in reality.
secondary_definitions: ( slang , MLE , transitive ) To think about , especially deeply ( “ profoundly ” ) ; to consider .
